{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1646061109.8925157", "card_id": "Q_519072580", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 4832}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "普京表示俄罗斯战略威慑力量转入特殊战备状态，这意味着什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当地时间 27 日，俄罗斯总统普京会见俄罗斯国防部长绍伊古和总参谋长格拉西莫夫时表示，西方对俄罗斯不仅在经济上进行遏制，而且某些领导人的发言越来越具有侵略性，因此命令俄罗斯战略威慑力量进入特殊战备状态。（央视新闻）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-bdd2a3ea95637a60ffa217fc18f50212_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5817 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/519072580"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI8I+dx6WGjrtIEAMaCDc3NjMxMjY2IKH47ZAGMPAEOMxWQAByCTUxOTA3MjU4MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1646061109.8932145", "card_id": "Q_519133946", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1381}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "俄罗斯已开始组织从欧洲撤离本国公民，这释放了哪些信号？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当地时间 27 日，俄罗斯航空运输局表示，已开始组织从欧洲各国撤离俄罗斯公民，目前正在进行资料收集和统计，具体时间和行程将根据具体情况确定。 "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-148e671d3144d050bd5e2697877b720e_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3753 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/519133946"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI8I+dx6WGjrtIEAMaCDc3NjQ0OTEwILbI75AGMOIBOLgiQAFyCTUxOTEzMzk0NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1646061109.8938498", "card_id": "Q_518898620", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 959}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么大多数西部年轻人宁愿在成都拿 4-5k 月薪合租，也不去沿海拿高工资打拼？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-e23163b466da1f5d2213a2346c0c09c4_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3731 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/quest